title: ARUP Module 5 - Cleaning and Transforming Data
displayTitle: ARUP Module 5 - Cleaning and Transforming Data
body:
Before data can be used as part of a project, the quality and fitness for purpose of that data needs to be checked. There are three main stages in this process:

  1. Data cleaning
  2. Data transformation
  3. Exploratory data analysis 

This module examines the process of cleaning and transforming data ready for analysis. It should be noted that while data cleaning is the essential first step, exploratory data analysis may happen before or after data transformation.
